title: Mozart - The Last 10 String Quartets - Mosaiques Quartet
description:
Mozart: The Last 10 String Quartets.

Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart's last ten string quartets-the "Haydn Quartets," Nos. 14 - 19; the "Hoffmeister Quartet," No. 20; and the "Prussian Quartets," Nos. 21 - 23-performed by the Mosaiques Quartet and released by Alliance in 2003. This is a period instrument quartet and their performances are excellent.

Please enjoy.
